README
=============================================================================
just simulate the odds of the german lottery "Bingo! Die Umweltlotterie" :
http://www.lotto-niedersachsen.de/s/managed_html/536/index.html

bingo.pl : small perl scriptlet to do it

bingo.ods : sheet with simulated odds

A typical call gives (choose a terminal with 144 columns or more ) :

$> time ./bingo.pl -v 1 -n 10000000
create 10000000 tickets for 1 drawing:
    0x-Bingo    1x-Bingo    2x-Bingo    3x-Bingo    4x-Bingo    5x-Bingo
